   "body" : "Starting with commit d6af06d68aa, a block hash of all-zeros is invalid and will lead to a crash of the node. Can be tested by cherry-picking the test changes without the other changes.\r\n\r\nThe fix:\r\n\r\n* Removes the special value of all-zeros for the `from_snapshot_blockhash` and asserts that it is never zero\r\n* Adds an early-fail clause to avoid the crash",
